      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAGIC MANIA (3) boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten a nose (17.33) behind TERRELL BANNER at this track. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Can measure up this time. DESPICABLE PEDRO (2) made light work of a wide draw last time with a slick early sectional but gathered in and had to settle for the minors, finishing second (22.71) at Maitland over 400m. Well placed and gets his chance. LEVI DESIGN (4) broke from the inside draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only 1.75 lengths (17.48) behind Brailey Banner at this track. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Overdue and is among the main hopes. RUINATION (1) collected a minor prize last start at big odds and must be considered.",
